{
  "stem": "18778.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 217.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was on deck at that time also, but she took me away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, people were crowding around the rails, and she took me away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The passengers collected from their meager coinage and gave the sailor a reward for saving this man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the gestapo took note of the fact that a German sailor bothered to jump into the water to save a Jew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We left Havana with the accompaniment of the harbor patrol and a whole procession of cars that drove along the beach street, the ocean drive, and I guess it was one of the saddest days in people's lives when we left Havana.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "From there on in there were always notices posted on the bulletin boards near the elevators, which gave encouraging information.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Even if there was nothing to encourage, there was encouraging information.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We're in touch with this one and with that one and with this committee and that committee.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we will keep you informed, and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "All these documents were in my possession because of my father and are in the archives in Washington, DC at the Holocaust Museum.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I have copies of almost everything that I gave them, but they have the originals.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the committee not only was meeting with the captain, but they also organized patrols so there wouldn't be another suicide attempt.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because people were very desperate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Most of the men on board had been incarcerated as a result of the November pogrom.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And upon their release, they had to sign that they would leave Germany within a very short period of time, and that they would never divulge what they experienced in their incarceration, nor would they return to the Third Reich upon punishment of death.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so you can imagine that there was panic on board.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
